      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ON THE STRIP (5) finds it hard to break through. Filled a minor placings again last time when second (20.28) at this track making it three placings in a row. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Rates highly and will give a great sight. OUR SHERALEE (4) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 20.38 beating Lockaba Nitro. Deserves serious consideration again. SMOOTH PARADISE (7) placed last time (20.40) at this track in a Other, finishing third and beaten 4.5 lengths. Has two wins already from this draw. Looks a key chance on best figures. BINGO QUEEN (8) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
